以下是详细的建立过程：

1. 准备ESP32和压电陶瓷传感器。

2. 将压电陶瓷传感器连接到ESP32的模拟输入引脚，通过采样模块采样传感器输出的模拟信号，将信号转换成数字信号后进行滤波和处理，得到心率信号数据。

3. 在ESP32上运行程序，使用蓝牙传输模块将数据进行传输。首先，需要在ESP32上安装BTStack库和BLE库。然后，通过配置代码，启用蓝牙模块并配对要连接的设备。具体过程如下：

```C++
#include <BTstack.h>
#include <BLEDevice.h>

// Set up BLE server
BLEServer *pServer = BLEDevice::createServer();

// Set up BLE service
BLEService *pService = pServer->createService(SERVICE_UUID);

// Set up BLE characteristic
BLECharacteristic *pCharacteristic = pService->createCharacteristic(
  CHARACTERISTIC_UUID,
  BLECharacteristic::PROPERTY_READ |
  BLECharacteristic::PROPERTY_NOTIFY
);

// Enable the BLE service
pService->start();

// Start advertising the BLE service
BLEAdvertising *pAdvertising = BLEDevice::getAdvertising();
pAdvertising->addServiceUUID(SERVICE_UUID);
pAdvertising->start();
```

4. 开始传输数据，将数据打包成JSON格式并通过BLECharacteristic发送到指定设备。具体过程如下：

```C++
// Pack the data into JSON format
const size_t capacity = JSON_OBJECT_SIZE(2);
DynamicJsonDocument doc(capacity);
doc["heart_rate"] = hr_data;
doc["timestamp"] = millis();
String jsonString;
serializeJson(doc, jsonString);

// Send the data using BLE
pCharacteristic->setValue(jsonString.c_str());
pCharacteristic->notify();
```

5. 如果需要将数据上传到云端或本地服务器，控制ESP32连接WiFi网络并使用HTTP/HTTPS等协议通过WiFi模块将数据上传到指定的服务器或云服务平台。具体过程如下：

```C++
// Connect to WiFi network
WiFi.begin(ssid, password);

while (WiFi.status() != WL_CONNECTED) {
  delay(1000);
  Serial.println("Connecting to WiFi...");
}

// Send the data using HTTP POST request
HTTPClient http;
http.begin("https://your-server.com/path/to/upload");
http.addHeader("Content-Type", "application/json");
int httpResponseCode = http.POST(jsonString);

if (httpResponseCode > 0) {
  Serial.println("Data upload successful");
} else {
  Serial.println("Data upload failed");
}

http.end();
```

通过以上步骤，可以实现通过ESP32进行压电陶瓷测量心率信号数据的传输，并且可以选择传输到蓝牙设备、云端或本地服务器。具体实现过程可以根据具体需求进行调整和优化。
